PURPOSE
Listen for 802.11 probe requests and log them to a SQLITE database

DISCLAIMER
You are responsible for your decisions and actions related to the use of this software. 
This software is provided AS-IS. USE AT YOUR OWN RISK

PREREQS
pyshark -- requires tshark

USAGE 
usage: wim.py [-h] [-d DATABASE] -i INTERFACE [-v] [-debug] [-disable]

Monitor

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -d DATABASE, --database DATABASE
                        Name of sqlite database
  -i INTERFACE, --interface INTERFACE
                        Interface to use for sniffing and packet injection
  -v, --verbose
  -debug, --debug
  -disable, --disable   Disable storing in SQLITE database. Suggest enabling
                        verbose output with -v
